{"tid":272858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"炒紅館表演既飛原來係不受法例監管！！（以後唔洗買正價飛了）","createTime":"2017-06-06T06:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T06:50:30.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c322150e77191352d94e48d68b30b04bc53003ca","tid":272858,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:19:46.000Z","msg":"7月舉行的英超亞洲盃，有原價600元及720元的正價門票遭「黃牛黨」炒賣，有門票交易平台炒至5,749元，淘寶網更有人開價8,888元，但足總副主席貝鈞奇表示，他們無法干預。 <br />\n<br />\n而《公眾娛樂場所條例》第6條雖然有監管「持牌公眾娛樂場所」的任何門票炒賣，但由於康文署轄下場，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">包括紅館及香港大球場</span></span>屬獲豁免發牌公眾娛樂場所，故不受有關法例監管，即使警方亦無法作出檢控。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-06-2017/38333\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-06-2017%2F38333&d=4SpXZaLj5ob%2B9IFCabkP2zM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=3f36ad2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-06-2017/38333</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017"},{"pid":"c102e370535b2c14397af61186f0c1b24e4efd52","tid":272858,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"推 推到班港豬個個都炒黃牛飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dad348151836c5e4adf91771b36d1e6c14164a","tid":272858,"uid":113681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"主辦單位肯搞實名制就解決問題啦。"},{"pid":"a6fd7161f57d36baa094ded4192b2404555fc847","tid":272858,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:40:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5672a7d7b6aa929f947fef57ed8f246cbf91b6db","tid":272858,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"港柒除左炒賣就冇野叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}